<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card" style= "background-color: #d6d6dd; border-radius: 200px">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%=image_tag "profile.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class ='skill'>
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized%>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I grew up in a house where computer time was limited. I'd tip-toe to the computer in the middle of the night to learn how to create the *perfect* MySpace layout. I memorized the steps to avoid floorboard creaks and typed ever so lightly to avoid awakening the grizzly upstairs with the tapping sound of an early 2000s HP keyboard.
        <br>
        <br>
        Late nights have become full days! I'm excited to incorporate my pre-teen MySpace passion with my experience in marketing, content creation, and finance as I transition into the abundant world of development.

        <br>
        <br>
        I'm Chaney. I love turning words into functionality and {#symbols} into design.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-success"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-success"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class"card card-block">
              Media Content Manager • <em>JT Marketing & Consulting</em>
            </div>

            <div class"card card-block">
              Financial Services Tax & Retirement Professional • <em>E*TRADE Financial</em>
            </div>

            <div class"card card-block">
              Teller • <em>Wells Fargo Bank</em>
            </div>

            <div class"card card-block">
              Personal Assistant to the VP • <em>Ideal Living Management</em>
            </div>

          </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class"card card-block">
              Bottega Technical Institute • <em>Full Stack Web Development</em>
            </div>

            <div class"card card-block">
              Utah Valley University • <em>In Progress : BS Communications</em>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>